{"tid":2363669,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"口罩害死動物 污染海洋咁大件事點解冇人講？","createTime":"2021-01-12T11:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T11:35:26.000Z","uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e89199db791117ff0da03e4f5d83433f648468","tid":2363669,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:24:53.000Z","msg":"【外電消息】<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎期間，各國紛紛強制在公共場所戴口罩防疫，也可以經常發現在人行道、水道與海灘發現用後即丟的一次性外科手術口罩，但這種拋棄式口罩薄薄的防護材質，得要好幾百年才能分解。<br />\n<br />\n善待動物組織（PETA）人員福魯諾（Ashley Fruno ）：「口罩無法很快消失於自然環境，當我們丟棄後，這些東西會對環境與一同生活在地球的動物造成傷害。」<br />\n<br />\n巴西保育人士在被沖上岸的企鵝屍體胃內發現口罩，在邁阿密外海也有河豚因口罩而喪命；法國海洋清潔行動（Operation Mer Propre）去年9月在鄰近地中海的鹹水潟湖，發現一隻困死於口罩裡的螃蟹。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：Op&eacute;ration Mer Propre<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iosmXCV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiosmXCV.jpg&h=48b740de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f437b1269f8d2a71ee420a5bc45838da3ebe0162","tid":2363669,"uid":110851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:25:44.000Z","msg":"冇人講咪⋯"},{"pid":"95407002ff350f819cd1bb29fabfca71e5f10b73","tid":2363669,"uid":310399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:26:16.000Z","msg":"咁佢想點？"},{"pid":"ca68a53845496b1182999944069b1a1315fa4122","tid":2363669,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:28:02.000Z","msg":"環保撚係咁架啦，一危害到自己既利益就乜撚都我睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae67e09f0b3ccddaddff56764cd16fc96a30a5a","tid":2363669,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:28:54.000Z","msg":"烤爹魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e8c26ce681130f4c076c9354874131924014f4","tid":2363669,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"估吓去到疫情完嘅時候全人類用咗幾多口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2341243\" data-auto-link target=\"_bl